Xu Fengnian.

344
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:57,830
Jangan bangun, kau tak pakai baju.

345
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,540
Kembalikan padaku.

346
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,590
Kita sudah sepakat.

347
00:30:08,110 --> 00:30:11,440
Kau boleh membunuhku, jika
gagal, maka harus bayar uang.

348
00:30:11,790 --> 00:30:12,990
Kemarin malam sudah gagal, 'kan?

349
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:17,640
Aku datang menagih.

350
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:21,960
Jangan berlebihan.

351
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:25,830
Kau ambil berapa banyak?

352
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:34,870
Menabunglah dengan baik.

353
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:42,830
Ayo.

354
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,640
Temani aku pancing ikan.

355
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,240
Tidak mau.

356
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,960
Kubayar kau.

357
00:30:57,110 --> 00:30:58,440
Jika kau tidak mau, akan kusimpan.

358
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,370
Kuberikan setelah di tepi danau.

